room_title: Escape room "Witching Hour" by Legendary Escape Rooms in Chicago
room_address: 42 W New York St Aurora, IL 60506
room_description: You and your friends discover a mysterious cabin. You enter the cabin and undo a spell that conjures a demon. Surrounded by trinkets and artifacts of a powerful witch, you and your friends must find the missing pages to reverse the curse and escape alive!
